oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry Stars (proof)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand Ole Opry (Radio program); Metal photoplates; Makeready;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color half sheet (black on white) announcing WSM Grand Ole Opry stars with text from a Wally Fowler and Milton Estes show at the City Auditorium on November 26 printed on top, which is known as an "over print." It is possible the poster is a proof or make-ready. Poster features metal photoplates of two performers.
